! Nelson & Langer (1999, ApJ 524, 923) simplified C–O network in KIDA-style format
! only columns starting with "*" are used by the code
!   *Reactants  *Products     *alpha     *beta      *gamma     F        g      err *itype Tmin  Tmax *frml  *ID ni r 

! Cosmic-ray ionization (H2 CR rate taken to be 1.0; k_H2 = zeta_cr)
H2         CR                     H3+        e-         H                                            1.000e+00       0.000e+00  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  1  -9999   9999  1     1 1  1
He         CR                     He+        e-                                                      5.667e-01       0.000e+00  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  1  -9999   9999  1     2 1  1

! Ion–molecule reactions (two-body, constant rates; k = alpha)
H3+        C                      CHx        H2                                                     2.000e-09  0.000e+00  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  4  -9999   9999  3     3 1  1
H3+        O                      OHx        H2                                                     8.000e-10  0.000e+00  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  4  -9999   9999  3     4 1  1
