C+         H2                     CHx        H                                                      4.000e-16  0.000e+00  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  4  -9999   9999  3     8 1  1
C+         OHx                    HCO+                                                              1.000e-09  0.000e+00  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  4  -9999   9999  3     9 1  1

! Neutral–neutral
O          CHx                    CO         H                                                     2.000e-10  0.000e+00  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  4  -9999   9999  3    10 1  1
C          OHx                    CO         H                                                     1.004e-10  5.000e-01  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  4  -9999   9999  3    11 1  1

! Electron recombination 
He+        e-                     He                                                               2.338e-12 -6.400e-01  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  8  -9999   9999  3    12 1  1
