M+         e-                     M                                                                9.325e-12 -6.500e-01  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  8  -9999   9999  3    16 1  1

! Charge-transfer (constant rate)
H3+        M                      M+         e-         H2                                         2.000e-09  0.000e+00  0.000e+00 2.00e+00 0.00e+00 logn  5  -9999   9999  3    17 1  1

